Class Teacher

java.lang.Object
Teacher
public class Teacher
extends java.lang.Object
This Teacher class represents a substitute teacher to be used by the corresponding Driver program. Documentation for basic accessor and mutator methods is omitted.
Author:
Theodore Campbell, 3461781, Abdur Rahman Chowdhury, 3690692

    • makeUnavailable

      public void makeUnavailable​(java.lang.String date, char time)
      c: This method creates and assigns a special shift object with no location or absent teacher to represent only a date and time in which this substitute is unavailable. Methods trying to assign this substitute for the specified time won't be able to.
      Parameters:
      date - - the date of the unavailability.
      time - - the time of the unavailability.
